ProtoResult:
. "A series $\sum a_n$ converges if and only if for every 
   $\epsilon>0$ there is an integer $N$ such that 
   \begin{equation} |a_n+a_{n+1}+\cdots+a_m|<\epsilon \quad 
   if\quad m\ge n\ge N. \end{equation}"
